# NOTE: PDFs under /public/resources ARE tracked so the `public` store deploys
# with the app (seed samples + any files you import to the public store). For a
# large library prefer the Supabase store (CONTENT_STORE=remote) to keep the
# repo light — then the PDFs live in Supabase, not git.

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
